{"tid":935623,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"完美胸部 史上最性感聖誕老人登場","createTime":"2018-12-10T07:14:08.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-10T09:17:26.000Z","uid":147522,"like":23,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"559fd9f27da9ee3245b056bd6117802209b60cb4","tid":935623,"uid":147522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-10T07:14:08.000Z","msg":"聖誕老人就一定得是胖嘟嘟的白髮白鬍老人嗎？英國一個熟齡約會網站最近扭轉傳統的聖誕老公公形象，塑造出一個「英俊性感」版本的聖誕老人，大秀胸肌和胸毛，該網站創辦人說︰「誰說聖誕老人不可以是性感象徵？」<br />\n<br />\n約會應用程式Lumen最近請來58歲模特兒奧查德（Paul Orchard）擔任「新版聖誕老人」，其中一張廣告照片中，只見他穿上紅色三件式西裝在書牆前雙手插袋，瀟灑靜立，散發著古典優雅的紳士魅力；另一張照片中的他赤裸上身，顯露健碩身材，手臂上還有醒目的刺青。奧查德與傳統聖誕老人相似的地方，可能就只有一頭銀髮和鬍子。奧查德說︰「這次扮演聖誕老人是我工作上最有趣的一部份，我很喜歡這些照片。證明即使年紀大了也可以繼續追求樂趣。」<br />\n<br />\nLumen的用戶主要為50歲以上人士，該公司先前調查發現，1/5受訪英國女性認為聖誕老人有吸引力。當被問到聖誕老人有什麼吸引之處，71%說是他的「友善外表」，63%說是「他的笑容」，60%說喜歡他的「好脾氣」。 說到外貌，20%女性認為他的鬍子迷人，17%喜歡他的一頭銀髮，9%人喜歡他健碩的身材。基於調查結果，Lumen塑造出這個性感聖誕老人形象。<br />\n<br />\n約會專家兼Lumen共同創辦人萊斯特（Charly Lester）說：「很明顯不少50歲或以上人士，都覺得(傳統)廣告搞錯了。我們想透過一位十分英俊的聖誕老人，用有趣、性感、貼地氣的聖誕廣告來表達。誰說聖誕老人不可以是性感象徵？年紀增長不會減低你的吸引力。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fWyWm00.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfWyWm00.png&h=4f4626dd&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4a1594c1290bc1052f88ef209466f2a938accf88","tid":935623,"uid":51717,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-10T07:22:53.000Z","msg":"連登例牌回覆：<br />\n<br />\n好想幫佢含<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a9ac6242d1c0bf040bc2d3d2fab67b86a2b6d3c7","tid":935623,"uid":12143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-10T07:34:01.000Z","msg":"正啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"abc6f743b7f9b7b3ad66fd60f356e96ac3d828a4","tid":935623,"uid":12269,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4a1594c1290bc1052f88ef209466f2a938accf88","tid":935623,"uid":51717,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-10T07:22:53.000Z","msg":"連登例牌回覆：<br />\n<br />\n好想幫佢含<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-10T07:40:17.000Z","msg":"好想你幫我含<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ddbeef7251d9514e24c283e7d8b0842021c9f5e","tid":935623,"uid":147522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"abc6f743b7f9b7b3ad66fd60f356e96ac3d828a4","tid":935623,"uid":12269,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4a1594c1290bc1052f88ef209466f2a938accf88","tid":935623,"uid":51717,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-10T07:22:53.000Z","msg":"連登例牌回覆：<br />\n<br />\n好想幫佢含<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-10T07:40:17.000Z","msg":"好想你幫我含<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-10T08:11:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2bdfabc51a56d312ef94d48a40cf9a0d40e7b243","tid":935623,"uid":59788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-10T09:17:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}